Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.30,0:00:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有卖哦 莫古索
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.22,0:00:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早饭很丰盛哦
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.43,0:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索还真是喜欢做饭 今天也不是你当班
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢做还是喜欢吃
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.23,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,都喜欢吧
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.41,0:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得我以前好像很喜欢做饭给谁吃
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能让那个人高兴就是另一回事了
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.38,0:01:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你说高兴...大家都很高兴啊
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.84,0:01:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为莫古索的饭很好吃
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.63,0:01:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.85,0:01:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把大家叫起来
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛啦 只是一场事故罢了
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是场不幸的事故
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要什么样的事故墙才会穿啊
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事...我怎么可能知道
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 别说了蓝德 你也赶紧道歉
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.84,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了又没看到你 还这么罗里吧嗦干什么
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在试图看了好吗
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是犯罪 我要去叫警察了
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城里才没有警察呢
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.18,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来别带毛巾泡澡啊 真不符合礼仪
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去叫
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么知道
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.11,0:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能去想看你这种平胸
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别说人平胸
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.87,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你还是说实话比较好 现在说梦儿还不会生气
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.71,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那啥啦...我试着爬了爬浴场的墙他就坏了
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说我们和墙都还太年轻了
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说不会生气的吗 而且到最后也没看到啊
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再跟蓝德说话了
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,气氛真不好
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还有点温热
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定能追上
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,两只...不对 是三只
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是单只的波布林啊
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是波布林 是哥布林
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.01,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露可能要花上点时间
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 真是对不起
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔倒是没关系
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.35,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个没关系不是说被你看也没关系
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.15,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就算看了你也会道歉
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过也不是道歉就能算了的事
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.24,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,被看光了还是被看光了
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.11,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要说那么多遍被看光了
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什么没关系呢
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你问我...那个...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是不太好吧
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不好啊 哈尔
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么怎么办
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只能回去了 回欧鲁达那
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真是劳工吾二啊
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 嗯...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.19,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且说下 是劳而无功
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,梦儿记错了吗
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔的啦
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没能赚到呢
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.75,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,之后的一天 再之后的一天 再再后的一天
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都没怎么赚到
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.34,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是没怎么 不如说是接近零
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,其实说白了 就是零
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.85,0:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,原本穿着的衣服一下子就不能穿了
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.15,0:07:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,因为本来就不是为了爬山 和哥布林战斗设计的
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.28,0:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此我们也还是缝缝补补地在用着
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真想要条新裤子
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个世界的衣服很贵
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.04,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是贵\N不如说使我们太穷了 什么都买不起
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,连换洗的衣服都买不起
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们就像这样晚上洗内裤 睡觉时不穿
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,早上起来穿在装备里面
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此也比没有的好
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.31,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好 明天目标 要打到哥布林买内裤
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我已经洗好了
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有隐隐的香甜气味
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.63,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不穿就行了 但是女孩子呢
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 这样我会沦为蓝德的同类的
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...这...这是...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 哈尔
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,晚...晚安
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 这这副打扮太不妙了
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在宿舍里穿成这样走来走去太不好了
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 太不行了
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她们也太没有防备了
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不...不行 这样下去我真的要...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.14,Default-top,,0,0,0,,你在干啥 哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不没什么
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.10,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.81,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,下这么大雨 洗了也不会干的
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早上洗不好吗
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道明天会不会放晴啊
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.94,0:09:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,话说不是你跟我说太臭了 偶尔要洗洗的吗 哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.11,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 所以说 今天洗了我也后悔了
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.66,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不能让这个鬼畜大王去女生那里
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的使命感驱动着我
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 有道理 而且也很麻烦
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 没错
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.21,0:10:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想着女生可能在才来的
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别笑这么恶心
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真危险
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.89,0:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那副打扮对眼睛伤害太大了 下次装作随意地提一下吧
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.89,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不 还是提一下吧
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.15,0:10:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,达姆洛曾经是巴拉巴吉亚第二大的城市
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经是比欧鲁达那大得多的城市
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.83,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的达姆洛成了哥布林的大本营
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.29,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在被称作新街区的地方附近的哥布林 又强数量又多
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们完全打不过
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.34,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们来到了被称为旧街区的这片区域
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.26,0:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,需找落单的哥布林
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.35,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这样也比在森林里遭遇的机会要多得多 但危险也更大了
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一只哥布林 好像睡着了
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好 上吧
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索的盔甲怎么弄都会发出声音
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.91,0:11:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以由我和哈尔希洛 蓝德先接近
Dialogue: 100,0:11:27.99,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能在不吵醒哥布林的情况下接近它 我们就一口气解决它
Dialogue: 100,0:11:33.29,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果把它吵醒了
Dialogue: 100,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,梦儿就射箭 席赫露就用魔法从远处掩护我们
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索快速向前
Dialogue: 100,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,变成正面对抗就采取上次那样的阵型
Dialogue: 100,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别让它逃走 所有人一起上去包围
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕
Dialogue: 100,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,趁睡觉时偷袭 原来就这么简单啊
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要挖个手指下来
Dialogue: 100,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,外斯外斯
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.75,0:12:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 好厉害 最高记录啊
Dialogue: 100,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这只是第二只
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有4银那么多
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.01,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还没结束 要继续下去
Dialogue: 100,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是偶然碰上了简单的 但不一定每次都能这么顺利
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要大意 继续寻找下一个猎物吧
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别说这么死板的话
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.40,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,难得大胜一场 多亏了本大爷
Dialogue: 100,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候该高兴一下吧
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要高兴也行
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德干得很不错
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.87,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,用剑刺哥布林 挂着冷酷笑容的我 很有黑暗骑士的感觉吧
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你只是很拼命吧
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.84,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴 我可决定了 你的眼睛朝哪看呢 哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 100,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是那里吗 是在那里吗
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你一副眼睛都睁不开的样子我都没发现
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个梗玩够了吧
Dialogue: 100,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给点反应啊 这时候要给点反应 我很寂寞的
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一个梗玩三遍烦不烦啊
Dialogue: 100,0:13:18.23,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}打倒了敌人 有了收入
Dialogue: 100,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,队伍里的气氛活跃了起来
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底 我想大家是都很不安
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.12,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不知何时 我们也开始像义勇兵那样思考 行动了
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.71,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,之后 我们专找单独行动的哥布林打
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.51,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再达姆洛 我们也遇到过五只以上的集团
Dialogue: 100,0:13:54.89,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,连两只我们都要苦战一番 更别提五只了
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.52,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这样\N画着简易地图走遍达姆洛的工程还是很开心
Dialogue: 100,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还没去过
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,自然地有了目的 也能认路
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.24,0:14:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,踏入地图上没画出来的地方时 我心跳不已
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,走在地图上有的地方 让我很开心
Dialogue: 100,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,30 铜
Dialogue: 100,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,30？这是二手的吧
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,15铜的话我会考虑下
Dialogue: 100,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,新品能卖100铜呢
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,28铜
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.85,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,20铜我就能买了 我还想买点别的呢
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,25铜  不能再少了
Dialogue: 100,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 100,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃 这太好吃了
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,叫什么来着
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么 不是索尔佐吗
Dialogue: 100,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃 索尔佐好吃
Dialogue: 100,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我一杯
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.25,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露
Dialogue: 100,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱...抱歉 我还有点
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你想让他来跟你说话的吧
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,刀刃都卷起来了
Dialogue: 100,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你发现了？
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.30,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现干什么都得保养好武器
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不然没法安心
Dialogue: 100,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我能懂
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.64,0:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,会这么想的我们 你觉得不是已经有点义勇兵的样子了吗
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.31,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样子不样子的 我们不就是义勇兵吗
Dialogue: 100,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然还只是见习的
Dialogue: 100,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不错啊
Dialogue: 100,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德砍价砍得太厉害 让我心惊胆战的
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 砍那点不是很正常吗
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我还嫌少了呢
Dialogue: 100,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,买这么多吃的 吃不完会烂的
Dialogue: 100,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,烂掉我就给你
Dialogue: 100,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,武器衣服 食物也需要
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.92,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想等再攒点钱 去学新技能
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好吗
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,本大爷的暗黑剑要越来越锋利了哦
Dialogue: 100,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么锋利不锋利 现在都只有一个技能吧
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.85,0:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在磨练这个技能 超努力地磨练着呢 闪闪发光到都成黑闪闪了
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是买的吗
Dialogue: 100,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是自己做的
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你雕的吗 意外地手很巧嘛 莫古索
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不是都能拿去卖了
Dialogue: 100,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我没这个打算
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因为雕刻的时候能平静下来
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我看 梦儿可能会想要
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这时候要提到梦儿
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.84,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,啰嗦 我只是这么觉得而已
Dialogue: 100,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔说
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有闲钱了
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.68,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,买套在宿舍里穿的衣服也不错吧
Dialogue: 100,0:17:29.90,0:17:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这...确实是不错
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 100,0:17:35.95,0:17:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯..
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.41,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露 这个发夹超可爱
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是...是吗
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.75,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露 你一直没和男生说话
Dialogue: 100,0:17:53.00,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,梦儿觉得差不多该稍微说两句了吧
Dialogue: 100,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...我努力看看
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.47,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也不用努力啦
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.35,0:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露一直不说话 梦儿会很担心的
Dialogue: 100,0:18:13.82,0:18:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力看看
Dialogue: 100,0:18:17.03,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 梦儿不太会去表达
Dialogue: 100,0:18:35.76,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 100,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不 谢谢你
Dialogue: 100,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么突然这么说
Dialogue: 100,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我是想说完全不一样的话题来着
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,事我要谢谢你们才对
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多谢我们
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为大家都是我的同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:19:12.67,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感激
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.63,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这么正地说 听起来可能有点假
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.30,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不觉得是假话
Dialogue: 100,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在受你照顾
Dialogue: 100,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要是马纳多不在的话 我们肯定就糟了
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,说不好已经挂了
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是彼此彼此
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.65,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要是没有哈尔希洛你们在 我也不知道自己会变成什么样
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么想 在这里独自一人都是活不下去的
Dialogue: 100,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.21,0:19:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你不要理解错我的意思
Dialogue: 100,0:20:00.34,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多的话要找同伴肯定是一抓一大把吧
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.09,0:20:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,像是拜托别人让你入队
Dialogue: 100,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我都没想过
Dialogue: 100,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能不太喜欢向别人低头
Dialogue: 100,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可能也不太擅长处理上下关系
Dialogue: 100,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah 我可能也是这样
Dialogue: 100,0:20:28.49,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我总觉得 自己不太适合跟大家做同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得没这回事
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.63,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这么觉得 但我也不能断言
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,确实我只知道来到这里以后的马纳多
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:52.14,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的马纳多怎么样都没关系啦
Dialogue: 100,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人会在意的
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的马纳多是我们的同伴 是队长
Dialogue: 100,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是不在的话我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 100,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,明天也要早起
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.80,0:21:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 马纳多的表情是什么样的 有点想看又不太想看
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在格林姆加尔的第二十三天
Dialogue: 100,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也习惯了红月
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.40,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,人能适应任何环境
Dialogue: 100,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么想着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:40.01,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(80,300)}[Episode 3]\N哥布林袋里\N装着我们的梦想吗
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.91,0:23:37.95,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\1c&H0078F0&}[Episode 4]\N{\fs48\1c&H0078F0&}前往灰尘飞舞的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:53.20,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}The clock strikes half past five
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:56.17,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}Need to go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:14:02.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}Seems like that I always cause a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:08.23,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}Ready to finish up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:10.77,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}Run out the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:19.12,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}but it seems too late... I did it again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.24,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}Someone calls me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.85,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}here comes another thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:27.08,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}I am not ready for that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.86,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}leave me alone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.40,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}The rain will go on and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:35.46,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}Maybe I just need to stay away from it all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}so please let me go
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:41.64,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}I close my eyes and I think back
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.64,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}to the times life was
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.89,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}much more simpler
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.89,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}With friends right here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:51.69,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}We'd sing 'til the sun comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:06.37,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}Open my eyes and you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.46,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}stand before me with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.46,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}as I drop my bag
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:12.60,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}Right on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:19.34,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}We'd chat and laugh until our seeds grow all out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:23.95,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}And even though earth goes on and on and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:27.54,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}You being here brings me excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:31.20,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}And even though the seeds grow on and on and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.32,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an8}You right here is joy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.90,0:02:06.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,擦り傷だらけの昨日を繰り返して
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.41,0:02:10.68,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,僕らは拓く希望の明日を
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.18,0:02:29.70,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,このちっぽけな両手に何が残ってるだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.70,0:02:35.59,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,仰いだ声は空へ散っていった
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.31,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,手に入れた現実は燻んでて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.49,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,目の前が見えなくなっても
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.49,0:02:45.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,一緒なら長く続くこの道を
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.78,0:02:49.26,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,進んで行ける
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.71,0:02:55.65,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,埃にまみれた絆を繋いでく
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.12,0:03:01.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,過去と未来背中合わせの僕らは
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.51,0:03:09.07,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,間違いだらけの答えを繰り返して
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.07,0:03:14.33,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,光を求め手を伸ばすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.13,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,何度だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:14.42,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,つめたい雨上がりの
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.90,0:02:06.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,遍体鳞伤的昨日 循环上演
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.41,0:02:10.68,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,我们要开拓 希望的明天
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.18,0:02:29.70,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,在这双空无一物的手中 还残留下些什么
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.70,0:02:35.59,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,抬头仰望声音消散于天空
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.31,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,得到的现实熏得焦黑
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.49,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,即使看不清前方
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.49,0:02:45.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,大家一起便能大步前进
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.78,0:02:49.26,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,走在这条漫长的道路上
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.71,0:02:55.65,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,串联起满是尘埃的羁绊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.12,0:03:01.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,过去与未来 我们背靠背
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.51,0:03:09.07,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,重复着错误不断的答案
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.07,0:03:14.33,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,渴求着光芒伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.13,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:14.42,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,冰冷的雨停后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:20.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,试着触碰干渴的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:27.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,如同冒芽的花一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:33.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,感情的碎片 满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:46.09,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,手中得到的 你的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:55.10,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,成为宝物 将我引导向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:23:05.02,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,一直 追赶着你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:10.54,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,是从何时开始的呢 变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:17.63,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,彷徨在这浩淼的世界 我始终坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:25.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,在旅途尽头 一定能找到 我所探寻之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:20.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,渇いた空気ふれてみたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:27.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,芽生える花のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:33.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,想いのかけら溢れてくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:46.09,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,この手に貰えた君のぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:55.10,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,宝物になる未来へ導いてくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:23:05.02,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,ずっと君の声を追いかけていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:10.54,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,いつからなんだろう強くなったね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:17.63,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,広い世界探したものは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:25.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,旅路の果てにきっと見つかるから
